00:55:22.578 --> 00:55:26.916 line:90% position:50% align:center
Let’s examine how they did that
and what it means for us.

00:55:26.916 --> 00:55:29.585 line:90% position:50% align:center
What did they do to make their

00:55:29.585 --> 00:55:32.296 line:90% position:50% align:center
