00:55:32.296 --> 00:55:35.174 line:90% position:50% align:center
Well, Max and Irene had to ask themselves

00:55:35.174 --> 00:55:38.010 line:90% position:50% align:center
what was going on in their kids’ lives.

00:55:38.010 --> 00:55:41.097 line:90% position:50% align:center
What topics could they
discuss at family worship

00:55:41.097 --> 00:55:44.058 line:90% position:50% align:center
